content: अक्षुण्ण {%<ab>a.</ab>%} [न. त.] {@--1@} Unbroken uncurtailed. {@--2@} Not conquered or defeated, successful; अक्षुण्णोनुनयः <ls>Ve. 1. 2.</ls> {@--3@} Not trodden or beaten, unusual, strange; अभीक्ष्णमक्षुण्णतयातिदुर्गमं <ls>Śi. 1. 32</ls> being not practised or experienced. {@--4@} Inexperienced, not expert.
